00:24:21.650 --> 00:24:22.640
It's amazing.

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:23.570
They check now.

00:24:23.570 --> 00:24:25.100
But no one checked
back then, and I

00:24:25.100 --> 00:24:27.230
was able to interview
these very important people

00:24:27.230 --> 00:24:28.700
and learn something
and allow them

00:24:28.700 --> 00:24:29.850
to contribute their voices.

00:24:29.850 --> 00:24:33.020
We made a movie, and the
movie went through theaters.

00:24:33.020 --> 00:24:35.270
Now I'm two years in.

00:24:35.270 --> 00:24:38.720
My music career is way
behind me at this point.

00:24:38.720 --> 00:24:42.250
And then we make some websites,
like Slavery Footprint.

00:24:42.250 --> 00:24:44.710
And then we make
some documentaries,

00:24:44.710 --> 00:24:46.090
and on and on it goes.

00:24:46.090 --> 00:24:47.830
And people continue
to get involved.

00:24:47.830 --> 00:24:50.530
And then we made
