00:33:19.530 --> 00:33:21.090
So thank you.

00:33:21.090 --> 00:33:23.880
So, Ben is the one
that set this up.

00:33:23.880 --> 00:33:26.030
Thank you so much.

00:33:26.030 --> 00:33:27.631
Your love.

00:33:27.631 --> 00:33:29.130
This is somebody
who found his riot,

00:33:29.130 --> 00:33:30.510
and is a living
example of someone who

00:33:30.510 --> 00:33:31.800
makes a difference
every day, and I

00:33:31.800 --> 00:33:32.930
want to thank you for that.

00:33:32.930 --> 00:33:34.090
You know, shake it off.

00:33:34.090 --> 00:33:35.207
You're just doing--

