00:41:02.340 --> 00:41:03.640
there's some books in the back.

00:41:03.640 --> 00:41:04.760
There's books online.

00:41:04.760 --> 00:41:06.820
"A Selfish Plan to
Change the World."

00:41:06.820 --> 00:41:07.566
Thanks, man.

